ADDA CORP June Sales Fall 0.59% (Table) : 3071 TT

-- B y   J a n e t   O n g
-- 
2011-07-08T08:48:45Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-08/adda-corp-june-sales-fall-0-59-table-3071-tt.html
ADDA CORP (3071)  said unconsolidated sales
in June fell 0.59% to NT$265,825,000 from NT$267,414,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  6/2011           6/2010
Sales            265,825          267,414    
YOY%              -0.59%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           1,513,105        1,543,211   
YOY%              -1.95% 
=================================================================
 